     H            Y.
     F** AB#RFV *************************************
     F*  CHECK BARCODE                              *
     F*        POSTING                              *
     F*                                             *
     F*                                             *
     F************************************* AB#R3Z **
     FAB#PL76 UF  E           K        DISK
      *---------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80@NOHZ
     I                                        1   40PUNOYY
     I                                        5   60PUNOMM
     I                                        7   80PUNODD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80@REHZ
     I                                        1   40PURLYY
     I                                        5   60PURLMM
     I                                        7   80PURLDD
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *---------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PBARC   9
     C                     PARM           PSIRE   4
     C                     PARM           PSIRK   1
     C                     PARM           PNOHZ   8
     C                     PARM           PNOBN   20
     C                     PARM           PREHZ   8
     C                     PARM           FLAG    1
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    FLAG
     C           PBARC     CHAINAB#PL76              91
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE '9'       FLAG
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     PUSPDT
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     PUKODT
     C                     TIME           PUKOTN
     C                     MOVEL#USER     PUKOME
     C                     UPDATAB#PP751
     C                     MOVE PUNONY    PSIRE
     C                     MOVE PUNKOJ    PSIRK
     C                     MOVE @NOHZ     PNOHZ
     C                     MOVE PUBINN    PNOBN
     C           @REHZ     IFNE *ZERO
     C                     MOVE @REHZ     PREHZ
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    PREHZ
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
